1️⃣ Sequence Diagram: Manage Inventory

Actors / Objects:
Admin → Inventory Management System → Database

Admin → Inventory Management System : Add / Update Product
Inventory Management System → Database : Save Product Details
Database → Inventory Management System : Confirmation
Inventory Management System → Admin : Success / Failure Message


Purpose:
Handles product creation and updates in inventory.

2️⃣ Sequence Diagram: Sales Processing

Actors / Objects:
Sales Staff → System → Inventory → Database

Sales Staff → System : Enter Sales Details
System → Inventory : Check Stock Availability
Inventory → Database : Fetch Stock Data
Database → Inventory : Stock Information
Inventory → System : Stock Available
System → Database : Update Stock Quantity
System → Sales Staff : Sales Confirmation


Alternative Flow:

If stock is insufficient → System displays “Out of Stock” message.

3️⃣ Sequence Diagram: Stock Prediction

Actors / Objects:
System → Prediction Engine → Database

System → Prediction Engine : Request Stock Forecast
Prediction Engine → Database : Retrieve Historical Sales Data
Database → Prediction Engine : Sales Data
Prediction Engine → Prediction Engine : Analyze & Predict
Prediction Engine → System : Predicted Demand Report


Purpose:
Predicts future stock demand using historical data.

4️⃣ Sequence Diagram: Automatic Reorder Process

Actors / Objects:
System → Inventory → Supplier

System → Inventory : Monitor Stock Levels
Inventory → System : Stock Below Threshold
System → Supplier : Generate Purchase Order
Supplier → System : Order Confirmation
System → Inventory : Update Incoming Stock Status


Alternative Flow:

If supplier unavailable → System sends alert to Admin.
